body.description: ACDelco AAA Super Alkaline Batteries are equipped with advanced technology you can count on. ACDelco alkaline batteries perform better than the competition in high-drain and super high-drain devices, and they provide consistent discharge performance. ACDelco alkaline batteries are designed for long shelf-life with stainless steel pre-coating that prevents leakage and advanced ingredient formulation that helps maintain power over time. This recloseable storage pack includes 100 AAA batteries great for a variety of household devices, including clocks, remote controls, and toys. The 1.5-volt batteries contain no mercury or cadmium, making them a smart choice for your family and for the environment. A trusted national brand, ACDelco offers a wide variety of batteries you can count on, including alkaline batteries, lithium coin cell batteries, rechargeable batteries, and car batteries.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars ACDelco AAA Batteries: The Energizer Bunny's Long-Lost Cousins!
reviews.reviewText: Oh, the ACDelco 100-Count AAA Batteries, the unsung heroes of the remote control, the flashlight, and all those other gadgets that we can't live without! These batteries are like the Energizer Bunny's long-lost cousins – they just keep going and going (and going)!First of all, the sheer quantity of these batteries is a bit mind-boggling. With 100 of these little powerhouses at your disposal, you'll have more juice than a tropical fruit stand. It's like the universe saying, "Hey, you might not need that many batteries right now, but you never know when the zombie apocalypse will hit, and your TV remote will become your most valuable survival tool."Now, let's talk about the "Maximum Power Super Alkaline" part. It's like these batteries hit the gym and have been chugging protein shakes for months. When you pop them into your devices, they give it their all, as if they've been training for a battery marathon. I half-expect them to flex their tiny AAA muscles and shout, "I'm ready for action!"And the 10-year shelf life? That's like having a stash of secret power hidden away for a decade. It's the battery equivalent of a treasure chest. You could forget about them, discover them a decade later, and they'll still be raring to go, powering your remote with gusto.But here's where the comedy really kicks in – trying to find a place to store 100 batteries! It's like playing a real-life game of Tetris in your junk drawer. You'll find yourself rearranging your kitchen utensils, old receipts, and random knick-knacks just to make room for your battery bonanza.In conclusion, if you're looking for an abundance of power that's ready for anything life throws at you (or your TV remote), the ACDelco 100-Count AAA Batteries are your hilarious, over-the-top solution. Just be prepared for the challenge of finding storage space for all that battery awesomeness. It's like a comical adventure in itself!
